---
const DEMO_URL = "https://app.pullstok.com/?demo=1";
---

<section class="px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div
    class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] px-6 py-16 text-center sm:px-12"
    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a8bea 0%, #51ccee 55%, #ff9d00 130%);"
  >
    <!-- Blobs decorativos dentro del card -->
    <div class="blob absolute -left-10 -top-10 h-48 w-48 opacity-25" style="background: #ffffff;" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="blob absolute -bottom-12 right-0 h-56 w-56 opacity-20" style="background: var(--brand-red);" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="relative">
      <span class="badge bg-white/25 text-white backdrop-blur-sm">🚀 Empezá hoy</span>
      <h2 class="mt-5 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl">
        Dejá el cuaderno.<br />Tu negocio te lo agradece.
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg text-white/90">
        Sumate a los comercios que ya ordenaron su día a día con Pullstok.
        Te lleva cinco minutos arrancar.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href={DEMO_URL}
          class="btn w-full bg-white text-primary shadow-[0_12px_30px_-10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.35)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 sm:w-auto"
        >
          Probá el demo gratis
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-5 text-sm font-medium text-white/80">
        Sin tarjeta de crédito · Cancelás cuando quieras
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
